text: Jacques de Larosière de Champfeu (born 12 November 1929 in Paris) is a French central banker.. Larosière was Managing Director of the International Monetary Fund (IMF) from 17 June 1978 to 15 January 1987, and Governor of the Banque de France from 1987 to 1993. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Managing Directors of the International Monetary Fund Category:Politicians from Paris
